      "text": "set %x% = \u0022{\\\u0022port\\\u0022:8080}\u0022 as object/json",
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Stage 5 \u2014 the developer\u0027s escape hatch for a type-unknown value.\n\u0060as object/json\u0060 stamps the cast (shape \u0060object\u0060, encoding \u0060json\u0060);\nnavigation then materialises through the (object, json) reader and the\nfield resolves. Companion to NavigationOnTypeUnknown_AsksForAsType:\nthat one errors, this one shows the fix. Architect 829785fbe \u2014 json\nvalues are \u0060object\u0060-shaped, not \u0060text\u0060.",
